buyerAgent.name: San Diego Real Estate Agent Alex Saavedra Top One Percent in San Diego County

data.description: Beautiful 4-Bedroom Home at the End of a Cul-De-Sac in the Highly Desirable Bella Vida Community!  This 2-Story Stunner features upgrades throughout & stunning views from dual balconies in front & back. Open modern-concept layout w/elegant hardwood floors & new dual-pane windows throughout. Living room w/ tiled fireplace. Dining area w/ ceiling fan & sliding glass patio doors for al-fresco dining. Kitchen w/ hardwood cabinets & dine-in bar. Spacious Master Bedroom w/ private balcony offering panoramic mountain views. Large private backyard w/ covered patio, fruit trees, & grassy area - perfect for entertaining! Sunnova solar system. Central AC + hear. 2 car garage w/ plenty of driveway parking. Laundry room. Community amenities include a swimming pool, spa, & walking paths. Just a block away from Woodglen Vista Park / Cajon Park Elementary & just minutes to the best shopping, dining, & entertainment the area has to offer. Turnkey!
